title: Broken Lizard on Reservoir Dogs
itunes:title: Broken Lizard on Reservoir Dogs
description:
This week Chuck set a new record having all five members of Broken Lizard in the studio at once. It was a ton of fun, the guys were super nice and they all agreed to talk about Reservoir Dogs. Super Troopers II comes out today in theaters everywhere - support the guys!
